<li><a href="Wikipedia_Date_formattings" title="Wikipedia:Date formattings">Wikipedia:Date formattings</a></li>
<li><a href="http://meta.wikimedia.org/wiki/Help:Date_formatting_feature" class="extiw" title="m:Help:Date formatting feature">m:Help:Date formatting feature</a> at Meta</li>
